更新 learn-profile.schema.json 支持背景驱动和自定义扩展。

## 新增字段

### 1. background 字段

```json
{
  "background": {
    "work_experience": [
      { "role": "...", "company": "...", "technologies": [...] }
    ],
    "personal_projects": [
      { "name": "...", "technologies": [...] }
    ],
    "education": [
      { "degree": "...", "focus": "...", "technologies": [...] }
    ]
  }
}
```

### 2. custom_fields 扩展点

```json
{
  "custom_fields": {
    "additionalProperties": true
  }
}
```

### 3. evidence 结构优化

支持 adaptive-assessment 类型，包含 rounds 历史。

